    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring long-term structural and valvetrain integrity. The drivetrain features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension is enhanced with Bilstein B16 coilovers, providing adjustable damping and improved roll center geometry. While exhibiting minor aesthetic wear commensurate with its age, the car remains a high-performance analog machine with excellent compression across all cylinders and a sharp, communicative steering rack.",
