      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus RX 350 in Nebula Gray Pearl. This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the lower rear bumper from standard use. The interior is a haven of comfort, featuring Parchment leather seats that are free of rips or stains, though there is some light creasing on the driver-side bolster. Every electronic component, from the heated steering wheel to the intuitive navigation system and the premium audio, works exactly as it should. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs smoothly and has been serviced at 5,000-mile intervals\u2014we have the full service records available for your review. The tires were replaced last year and have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a non-smoker vehicle that has been garage-kept and cared for with pride. It\u2019s a dependable, stylish SUV that is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
